## ReadonlyKeys type

Get readonly property keys of T.

**Signature:**

```typescript
export type ReadonlyKeys<T> = {
  // remove undefined key
  [K in keyof T]-?: If<
    IsEquals<{ [P in K]: T[P] }, { -readonly [P in K]: T[P] }>,
    never,
    K
  >
}[Keys<T>]
```
**References:** [If](./types-kit.if.md)<!-- -->, [IsEquals](./types-kit.isequals.md)<!-- -->, [Keys](./types-kit.keys.md)

## Example


```ts
interface Props {
     readonly a?: number
     b: number
     readonly c: number
   }
   // Expect: 'a' | 'c'
   type Keys = ReadonlyKeys<Props>
```
